@startuml
!pragma layout smetana
title 08. Supervisor Agent Exception Handling (Implementation Optimized)

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

package "Entry Tier" {
  [supervisor_a2a_endpoint] as Controller
  [SupervisorA2aRequestValidator] as Validator
}

package "Domain/Execution Tier" {
  [SupervisorAgentService] as AgentService
  [SupervisorGraphExecutionService] as GraphExecution
  [DefaultA2AInvocationService] as Invoker
}

package "Error Mapping" {
  [SupervisorExceptionTranslator] as Translator
}

Controller --> Validator : validate_request
Controller --> AgentService : execute_task / handle_review_decision
AgentService --> Translator : map error to JSON-RPC

Validator --> ValueError : "Method not allowed"\n"Params required"
AgentService --> ValueError : "Snapshot verification failed"\n"State version mismatch"
Invoker --> RuntimeError : "Circuit Breaker OPEN"
Invoker --> ValueError : "Endpoint not found"
GraphExecution --> Exception : catch all -> publish_error

Translator --> JsonRpcResponse : ERROR (-32602, -32601, etc.)
Translator --> ReviewRejectResult : "reason_code": enum value

note right of Translator
Standardized Error Mapping:
- ValueError -> Invalid Params / Method Not Found
- RuntimeError -> Execution Failure / Circuit Breaker
- Integrity Result -> ReasonCode Mapping
- All stack traces are suppressed in A2A response
end note

note bottom of GraphExecution
Background worker error safety:
- Any exception in graph is caught
- Published to task event stream as 'error' event
- Prevents worker process crash
end note
@enduml
